{{Infobox dungeon |name = Mt Mortar |image = [[File:Mt Mortar.png|300px]] |caption = A map of Mt Mortar. |tokens = 5,500 |location = On route 42, east of Ecruteak City. }} '''Mt Mortar''' is a [[Dungeons|dungeon]] in [[Johto]]. It initially has 36 tiles arranged in a 6x6 square, including 6 chest tiles, 15 non-boss encounter tiles, and 1 boss encounter tile.
